sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant SA as Service A
    participant Policy as Validation Policy

    rect rgb(255,245,245)
    Note over C,SA: Before mitigation
    C->>SA: Send access token (aud=service-b)
    SA->>SA: Signature-only check
    SA-->>C: 200 allowed
    end

    rect rgb(245,255,245)
    Note over C,Policy: After mitigation
    C->>SA: Send access token (aud=service-b)
    SA->>Policy: Validate iss/aud/token_use/scope
    Policy-->>SA: reject audience mismatch
    SA-->>C: 401 denied
    end
